          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ph-blue font-semibold mb-1">September 21, 1972</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Martial Law Declared</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Ferdinand Marcos signed Proclamation No. 1081, placing the Philippines under Martial Law for over a decade.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: People Power -->
      <div class="gradient-border-card overflow-hidden flex flex-col animate-on-scroll-delay-1">
