            <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
              People Power
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">1986</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ph-blue font-semibold mb-1">February 25, 1986</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">People Power Revolution</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Millions of Filipinos gathered at EDSA, peacefully overthrowing the Marcos dictatorship and restoring democracy.</p>
        </div>
