          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ph-blue font-semibold mb-1">November 8, 2013</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Typhoon Yolanda (Haiyan)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">One of the strongest tropical cyclones ever recorded devastated the Visayas, killing over 6,000. Filipino bayanihan spirit shone in the aftermath.</p>
        </div>
