          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Carlos Yulo Wins Double Olympic Gold</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Gymnast Carlos Yulo won two gold medals at the Paris Olympics — the first Filipino to win Olympic gold in gymnastics.</p>
        </div>
